    "desc": "Mason's tools allow you to craft stone structures, including walls and buildings crafted from brick. Components: Mason's tools consist of a trowel, a hammer, a chisel, brushes, and a square. History: Your expertise aids you in identifying a stone building's date of construction and purpose, along with insight into who might have built it. Investigation: You gain additional insight when inspecting areas within stone structures. Perception: You can spot irregularities in stone walls or floors, making it easier to find trap doors and secret passages. Demolition: Your knowledge of masonry allows you to spot weak points in brick walls. You deal double damage to such structures with your weapon attacks. [Mason's Tools]",
